---
author: mlld
module: @mlld/ai
description: Simple wrappers for AI CLI tools (llm, claude, codex)
---

>> LLM CLI (simonw/llm) wrappers
@exec llm(system, prompt) = @run [llm "@prompt" -s "@system"]
@exec llm_media(system, prompt, media) = @run [llm "@prompt" -s "@system" -a @media]
@exec llm_tools(system, prompt, tools) = @run [llm "@prompt" -s "@system" --tool @tools]
@exec llm_all(system, prompt, parameters) = @run [llm "@prompt" -s "@system" @parameters]

>> Claude Code CLI wrapper
@exec claude(prompt) = @run [claude "@prompt"]

>> Codex CLI (OpenAI) wrappers
@exec codex(prompt) = @run [codex "@prompt"]
@exec codex_media(prompt, media) = @run [codex "@prompt" -a @media]

>> Clean API export
@data ai = {
  llm: {
    ask:   @llm,
    media: @llm_media,
    tools: @llm_tools,
    all:   @llm_all
  },
  claude: {
    ask:   @claude
  },
  codex: { 
    ask:   @codex, 
    media: @codex_media
  }
}